{"tid":871023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[生物題] 有冇人識分 藍定紫薯仔 同 紫蕃薯","createTime":"2018-10-21T14:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T02:30:45.000Z","uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f58cbe45b531bc8c7f17bde15db55ac9ca780a4","tid":871023,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adirondack_Blue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAdirondack_Blue&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2401d2dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adirondack_Blue</a><br />\n<br />\nGenus Solanum<br />\nSpecies Solanum tuberosum<br />\nCultivar 'Atom'<br />\nOrigin United States, 2003<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vitelotte\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FVitelotte&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bbf2d030\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vitelotte</a><br />\n<br />\nGenus Solanum<br />\nSpecies Solanum tuberosum<br />\nCultivar 'Vitelotte'<br />\nOrigin France<br />\n<br />\n頭兩種薯仔都係品種Solanum tuberosum<br />\n個外型都係普通薯仔咁<br />\n同埋香港好似冇得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港買到既紫薯好似係長條型成條蕃薯咁<br />\n<br />\n然後我又睇到依篇野<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/health/yanyan/44092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Fyanyan%2F44092&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b8e6c476\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/health/yanyan/44092</a><br />\n<br />\n不論在街市或超市，只要是紫肉薯仔狀物體，大部分都被標籤為「紫心番薯」。正如之前提過，其實大部分都是紫薯Sweet Potato。這個也難怪，因為我翻查過香港政府食物規格資料庫，官方也稱紫薯為紫心番薯。資料庫應用了一張紫薯圖片，英文名為Purple Sweet Potato。然而，甘薯的植物學名為Ipomoea Batatas，但中文名卻稱為「紫心番薯」。連政府都混淆了。<br />\n<br />\n怎樣分別：紫薯 vs 紫心番薯<br />\n<br />\n　　真正的紫心番薯，是屬於Dioscorea家族，而非Ipomoea。真正紫心番薯其實不常見，我走了幾間超市街市才找到。<br />\n<br />\n　　因為兩種植物都有多種顏色類別，所以不要單憑外皮顏色去辨別。<br />\n<br />\n　　紫薯，跟其他甘薯類別一樣，身形通常瘦長，外皮較平滑，頭尾最少有一端是尖尖的。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於紫心番薯，外皮通常像樹皮一般粗糙，我覺得簡直有點醜陋，身形較短而飽滿。兩者最大分別，就是用刀一切下去，紫心番薯比較乾身亦較粉身，但紫薯則相對軟滑。<br />\n<br />\n再上wiki睇下<br />\n<br />\nIpomoea batatas=<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sweet_potato\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSweet_potato&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=32e1651c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sweet_potato</a><br />\n<br />\nDioscorea alata=<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%82%E8%96%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258F%2582%25E8%2596%25AF&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=955f3a86\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%82%E8%96%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/224811_35b6145772b5d0372051fc58d6b4d2c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F224811_35b6145772b5d0372051fc58d6b4d2c5.png&h=1549224a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於香芋的名稱和顏色吸引，部份華人在製作芋頭批、芋頭酥等芋頭類食品時，會加入紫薯與芋頭混合作為餡料，來模仿參薯的顏色和味道，雖然沒有參薯的香味，但卻會稱作「香芋批」、「香芋酥」。現時部份華人食肆甚至會把芋頭直稱為「香芋」，例如把芋頭西米露稱為「香芋西米露」。但這些混用，卻使「香芋」一詞產生歧義，並產生一些實際問題。<br />\n<br />\n媽我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83545cf609790c44465669ab3e78ec48ead49057","tid":871023,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"e728bbcc460eeeb822f296cb2a19743b177c30e8","tid":871023,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}